                        <p><span class="fc-orange">What is Woomatch? </span></p>
						Woomatch allows you to connect with others who have the same interests as you. Woomatch is about you connecting with others and having fun. 
						
						
						   <p><span class="fc-orange">How Can I Register? </span></p> 
						You can registered by entering your information or via facebook. First click LOGIN and fill in the required information like your name, email, gender and password then press Register. The second possibility is to connect via your Facebook account by pressing the blue button LOGIN WITH FACEBOOK.
						
						
					 <p><span class="fc-orange">Can I watch the activities around me without having an account? </span></p> 
						Yes, the home page automatically suggests some activities in your area or you can change the city to see is out there. You can also search via the SEARCH ACTIVITIES bar at the top and we will suggested a few activity for you. You should register if you really want to see more activity or contact the person in charge.
						
						
			 <p><span class="fc-orange">			Want to know more about the concept? </span></p>  

						Press the DISCOVER button and watch the video.


				 <p><span class="fc-orange">		How does the search work? </span></p> 

						It can be done in 2 ways:
						
						Go on ACTIVITIES SEARCH bar on the header, type in what you want to search and we will give you suggestions; 
						Press ADVANCED SEARCH bar menu. You do a search based on a city, a specific date or period, an interest, a gender or an Age range. 

						The Advanced Search Function 

						We offer three results: The most popular, results near you and the latest and best activities. 


					 <p><span class="fc-orange">		Is it really free? </span></p> 

						Yes. You can use Woomatch for free. We are in a phase where we want you to enjoy all the functionality for free! So feel free to browse and post as much as you want. Make friends and go out have fun.
						 
